            <title><![CDATA[非常令人惊喜的插件：Onemark ；
一款让OneNote支持Markdown语法的插件，简洁、高效。
在OneNote 里写markdown的感觉太奇妙了。

当初在学校主力笔记软件是OneNo...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<br>非常令人惊喜的插件：Onemark ；<br>一款让OneNote支持Markdown语法的插件，简洁、高效。<br>在OneNote 里写markdown的感觉太奇妙了。<br><br>当初在学校主力笔记软件是OneNote。工作之后写文档主要为markdown语法。OneNote 就渐渐放弃了。但有了这个插件之后，可能OneNote 会再次成为我的主力笔记软件。遗憾的是不支持UWP版本。<br><br>官网https://onemark.neuxlab.cn/docs/<br><br>放几张图感受一下。<br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FnXaXRHM6ePjXZK4rrng_JDhxkYxv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FnXaXRHM6ePjXZK4rrng_JDhxkYxv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FnXaXRHM6ePjXZK4rrng_JDhxkYxv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FuduMoIEiOyUKrvFU2MLZKrC41Nrv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtblSQApoMk4l0WpgA1xTlR9ymphv2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtblSQApoMk4l0WpgA1xTlR9ymphv2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FtblSQApoMk4l0WpgA1xTlR9ymphv2.png"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FsFze2xVICEB3q8QLgX-RjG3UUZ2v2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FsFze2xVICEB3q8QLgX-RjG3UUZ2v2.png" type="image/png"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fs